Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:06.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1141,1053)}生きとるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:06.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1480,1053)}生きとるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:06.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1290,1053)}生きとるよ！
